@startuml
!include style.puml
skinparam arrowThickness 1.1
skinparam arrowColor MODEL_COLOR
skinparam classBackgroundColor MODEL_COLOR

Package Model <<Rectangle>>{
Interface ReadOnlyAddressBook <<Interface>>
Interface ReadOnlyUserPrefs <<Interface>>
Interface ReadOnlyCommandHistory <<Interface>>
Interface Model <<Interface>>
Class AddressBook
Class ReadOnlyAddressBook
Class CommandHistory
Class Model
Class ModelManager
Class UserPrefs
Class ReadOnlyUserPrefs

Class "{abstract}\nHandle" as Handle
Class UniquePersonList
Class Person
Class Name
Class Phone
Class Remark
Class Tag
Class Facebook
Class Instagram
Class Telegram
Class TikTok
Class Twitter
}

Class HiddenOutside #FFFFFF
HiddenOutside ..> Model

Model .d.> ReadOnlyAddressBook
Model .d.> ReadOnlyUserPrefs
Model .d.> ReadOnlyCommandHistory
ReadOnlyAddressBook -[hidden]r> ReadOnlyUserPrefs
ReadOnlyUserPrefs -[hidden]r> ReadOnlyCommandHistory

AddressBook .u.|> ReadOnlyAddressBook
UserPrefs .u.|> ReadOnlyUserPrefs
CommandHistory .u.|> ReadOnlyCommandHistory

ModelManager -u-> "1" AddressBook
ModelManager -u-> "1" UserPrefs
ModelManager -u-> "1" CommandHistory

ModelManager ....u|> Model
ModelManager --->"~* filtered" Person

AddressBook *--> "1" UniquePersonList
UniquePersonList --r> "~* all" Person

Person *----> Name
Person *----> Phone
Person *----> "*" Tag
Person *----> Remark

Person *--> Facebook
Person *--> Instagram
Person *--> Telegram
Person *--> TikTok
Person *-->Twitter

Facebook -d-|> Handle
Instagram -d-|> Handle
Telegram -d-|> Handle
TikTok -d-|> Handle
Twitter -d-|> Handle

@enduml
